# Design profile

Quiet liquid glass. Low profile. Low texture. Minimal. Easy.

## Do

- Calm cool mist canvas (`#EEF1F5`), soft ink (`#1C2128`), quiet steel accent (`#3E5A6B`)
- Glass chrome via `GlassSurface` / `expo-blur` — hairline borders, soft wash, whisper shadow
- One purpose per screen; generous spacing (`space` tokens); clear hierarchy
- Primary actions obvious; secondary actions visually quieter
- Use tokens from `src/theme` — never hardcode random brand colors

## Don’t

- No logo / wordmark chrome in-app UI
- No “AI product” look: purple/indigo gradients, neon glow, dark cosmic themes, pill clusters, emoji flourishes, multi-layer shadows
- No warm cream + terracotta + serif newspaper layouts
- No busy textures, gradients as decoration, inset media cards, floating badges on media
- Don’t card-wrap everything — glass only for bars, sheets, modals, key surfaces

## Motion

Soft press (`scale ~0.98`), short ease (~160–240ms). Presence, not noise.
